Drama as driver abandons coffin after disagreement with mourners             Weldon Kipkemoi  28th Apr 2019 16:33:40 GMT +0300 Weldon Kipkemoi  28th Apr 2019 16:33:40 GMT +0300 Weldon Kipkemoi   Mercy Muthoni is controlled after viewing the body of Antony Kioko at the Likoni ferry area in Mombasa County on Sunday ,028th April,2019.This is after a driver of a hearse hired to transport the deceased from Mombasa's Coast General Hospital Mortuary dropped it at the Likoni Ferry area and sped of following disagreements. [Welson Kipkemboi,Standard]  Mercy Muthoni is controlled after viewing the body of Antony Kioko at the Likoni ferry area in Mombasa County on Sunday ,028th April,2019.This is after a driver of a hearse hired to transport the deceased from Mombasa's Coast General Hospital Mortuary dropped it at the Likoni Ferry area and sped of following disagreements. [Welson Kipkemboi,Standard] Mercy Muthoni is controlled after viewing the body of Antony Kioko at the Likoni ferry area in Mombasa County on Sunday ,028th April,2019.This is after a driver of a hearse hired to transport the deceased from Mombasa's Coast General Hospital Mortuary dropped it at the Likoni Ferry area and sped of following disagreements. [Welson Kipkemboi,Standard] Mercy Muthoni is controlled after viewing the body of Antony Kioko at the Likoni ferry area in Mombasa County on Sunday ,028th April,2019.This is after a driver of a hearse hired to transport the deceased from Mombasa's Coast General Hospital Mortuary dropped it at the Likoni Ferry area and sped of following disagreements.              Register to advertise your products & services on our classifieds website Digger.co.ke and enjoy one month subscription free of charge and 3 free ads on the Standard newspaper. Register to advertise your products & services on our classifieds website Digger.co.ke and enjoy one month subscription free of charge and 3 free ads on the Standard newspaper. Digger.co.ke Related Topics Mombasa residents Coast G